<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<!-- HEAD -->
<%- include('../adminPartials/adminHead') %>
<!-- END HEAD -->
<body>
<!-- HEADER -->
<%- include('../adminPartials/adminHeader') %> 
<!-- END HEADER -->

<!-- MAIN -->
    <main class="container min-vh-100 pt-5">
        <h2 class="title-listado">LISTADO DE PRODUCTOS:</h2>
        <table class="table table-striped table-hover">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th scope="col">id</th>
                <th scope="col">Nombre</th>
                <th scope="col">Precio</th>
                <th scope="col">Categor√≠a</th>
                <th scope="col">Stock</th>
                <th scope="col" class="btn"></th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <% productos.forEach(producto => { %>
                <tr>
                <th scope="row"><%- producto.id %></th>
                <td><%- producto.name %></td>
                <td><%- producto.price %></td>
                <td><%- producto.category %></td>
                <td><%- producto.stock %></td>
                <td class="btn">
                    <a href="/admin/productos/editar/<%- producto.id %>" class="btn-edit">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square"></i>
                    </a>
                    <form action="/admin/productos/eliminar/<%- producto.id %>?_method=DELETE" method="post">
                    <button class="btn-delete" type="submit">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can"></i>
                    </button>
                    </form>
                </td>
                </tr>
            <% }) %>  
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </main>
<!-- END MAIN -->
<!-- FOOTER -->
<%- include('../adminPartials/adminFooter') %> 
<!-- END FOOTER -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>